                <h1>Who Owns DraftKings? A Quick Overview</h1>
                <p>DraftKings is a publicly traded company, co-founded by Jason Robins, Matthew Kalish, and Paul Liberman in 2012. Ownership is shared among numerous shareholders, including institutional investors and individual stockholders. The company's growth has made it a major player in the sports betting and fantasy sports industries.</p>
